title: Third Age: Divide & Conquer - Isengard #14 - More wood for the Fire
description:
Welcome back to the Divide and Conquer Campaign.  Isengard is growing and becoming a power house of a faction.  Soon not even Lord Sauron can stop us.  The time for Uruk hai is now!  Also we need more trees for our industrial power! Enjoy :D


Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/pixelatedapollo
How to send me battle replays: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nG3uZoDkCU
How to play Medieval 2 Online: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YGfItCMitPg
